ygData.subject: RE: OT - clip frame?
ygData.msgSnippet: If you look at the trees carefully u will see that it is clip such that some branches are closer than the actual tree.  The clip is what allow u to see things
ygData.messageBody:
If you look at the trees carefully u will see that it is clip such that some
branches are closer than the actual tree. The clip is what allow u to see
things in a distance realistically but it takes up more processing power
though to do it.

Your Friendly Rogue and Bard
Hammerpaw and Syren Wind
Champions of Norrath, The Rathe

-Faras
